573
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:12,998
we might die together.

574
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,700
Aren't you afraid?

575
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:16,820
Not at all!

576
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:18,240
Share weal and woe,

577
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:19,700
for good or for worse,

578
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,680
that's what partners do.

579
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:24,960
Even if it's death, if we face it together,

580
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:27,140
there's nothing to be afraid of.

581
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,983
I see.

582
00:40:30,983 --> 00:40:33,680
I was wrong.

583
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:35,520
We've gone through the obstacles.

584
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,720
We've had a great time.

585
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:39,965
As long as we're together, there's nothing to be afraid of.

586
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:45,840
Besides, it's 50-50 for you and for me.

587
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:49,080
Count me in, and it's a safe bet.

588
