589
00:40:53,700 --> 00:40:57,240
In the sea, I'm the best hunter in my tribe.

590
00:40:57,260 --> 00:40:59,640
I'm more experienced in hunting than you guys.

591
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:01,120
I have a plan.

592
00:41:01,120 --> 00:41:02,860
What's that?

593
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,838
